A cybersecurity company conducts a password cracking challenge on a laptop, while human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. Representatives from nonprofit organizations emphasize mission-driven career paths, and some students quietly rehearse elevator pitches against the wall. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance. The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage. The dean stops by to thank recruiters for supporting the university. An aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge, while healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos, and an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews during the event. Meanwhile, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.
